title: Before The Rise - Seed To Soil
description:
Formed in November of 2006 the Southern New Hampshire based band has made a lot of headway in a short amount of time. With a sound that manages to touch upon the Staind, Taproot and Alice in Chains explorations of melodic rock, with the metal intensity of the Deftones, Sevendust and Nonpoint.
